	<TextInfo>
		<Text Type="Business Summary" lastModified="2015-03-07T01:24:38">Burford Capital Limited is a Guernsey-based investment capital company. The Company is a provider of investment capital and risk solutions with a focus on the litigation and arbitration sector and the provision of litigation expense insurance. The Company provides a range of corporate finance and insurance solutions to lawyers and clients engaged in significant litigation and arbitration around the world. The Company has two operating business segments which include Litigation Investment and Litigation Insurance. Litigation Investment segment consists of litigation and arbitration-related investment activities anywhere in the world. Litigation Insurance segment consists of litigation insurance activities in the United Kingdom and Channel Islands.</Text>
		<Text Type="Financial Summary" lastModified="2016-01-25T03:01:50">BRIEF: For the six months ended 30 June 2015, Burford Capital Limited revenues increased 48% to $40.6M. Net income applicable to common stockholders increased 99% to $23.1M. Revenues reflect Litigation Investment segment increase of 64% to $30.7M. Net income benefited from UK acquisition decrease from $5.9M (expense) to $0K. Dividend per share remained flat at $0.02.</Text>
